{"tid":523982,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[JJ插雪] 5月北海道10日9夜自駕遊行程求插","createTime":"2018-01-09T06:26:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T04:42:52.000Z","uid":61535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8a46dd82a0dd7b0faed6755897a5d66bf8244b23","tid":523982,"uid":61535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:26:38.000Z","msg":"今年5月中會去北海道10日自駕遊<br />\n大約諗左去邊再訂酒店<br />\n求下各位巴絲比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDAY1<br />\n14:10 到達新千歲 &gt; 拎車去登別入住望樓noguchi<br />\n(諗住租OTS)<br />\n<br />\nDAY2<br />\n酒店食早餐 &gt; 地獄谷 &gt; 熊牧場或者海洋公園 &gt; 行下溫泉街 &gt; 住望樓noguchi<br />\n<br />\nDAY3<br />\n酒店食早餐加CHECK OUT &gt; 函館 &gt; 函館山睇下夜景 &gt; 返酒店<br />\n(未訂酒店,未諗食咩)<br />\n<br />\nDAY4<br />\n函館朝市 &gt; 金森紅磚倉庫 &gt; 五稜郭公園 &gt; 大門橫丁 &gt; 返酒店<br />\n(依日唔渣車OK?)<br />\n<br />\nDAY5<br />\n食早餐 &gt; 洞爺湖 &gt; 遊下周圍 &gt; 住溫泉旅館<br />\n(未諗住邊間)<br />\n<br />\nDAY6<br />\nCHECK OUT 再J下景 &gt; 狸小路或者札幌站行下街 &gt; 返酒店<br />\n(未諗邊間)<br />\n<br />\nDAY7 <br />\n場外市場 &gt; 余市睇下酒廠 &gt; 小樽運河+出拔小路 &gt;札幌<br />\n<br />\nDAY8 + DAY9<br />\n除左會去埋二條市場就諗唔到去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴絲可唔可以比下意見<br />\n(旭川+富良野? )<br />\n<br />\nDAY10<br />\n應該臨去機場之前行OUTLET比條女放下電 &gt; 17:15上機返香港<br />\n<br />\n食野既話應該會食湯咖哩,成吉思汗烤肉,拉面,居酒屋,海鮮依類<br />\n筆值就每人萬五到兩萬港紙"},{"pid":"b9c04d0bc75d00c3f1c3f5bb0663de6d1b41b64a","tid":523982,"uid":44783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:49:08.000Z","msg":"望樓noguchi <br />\n我都想試, 但一晚3000幾, 唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e687d1f2a186b58cf13e2d9d70a79dc68b1279e9","tid":523982,"uid":44783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T07:05:37.000Z","msg":"睇你行程其實每日都唔係玩好多野<br />\n好大部分時間都係渣車<br />\n<br />\nDay1,2 冇咩問題<br />\nDay3,5 登別來回函館5粒幾鐘, 要有心理準備好攰<br />\nDay5 想去洞爺湖可以住登別果陣玩即日來回, 換少日酒店<br />\nDay7 渣車去酒廠? 唔打算試飲? 去開小樽唔試三角市場?<br />\n<br />\n5月去富良野應該冇咩野睇<br />\n可以考慮下留函館耐D, 話哂渣咁耐車去"},{"pid":"7097a4e5f10a36e4a600711b15fac8c339b013b9","tid":523982,"uid":61535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e687d1f2a186b58cf13e2d9d70a79dc68b1279e9","tid":523982,"uid":44783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T07:05:37.000Z","msg":"睇你行程其實每日都唔係玩好多野<br />\n好大部分時間都係渣車<br />\n<br />\nDay1,2 冇咩問題<br />\nDay3,5 登別來回函館5粒幾鐘, 要有心理準備好攰<br />\nDay5 想去洞爺湖可以住登別果陣玩即日來回, 換少日酒店<br />\nDay7 渣車去酒廠? 唔打算試飲? 去開小樽唔試三角市場?<br />\n<br />\n5月去富良野應該冇咩野睇<br />\n可以考慮下留函館耐D, 話哂渣咁耐車去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T07:43:15.000Z","msg":"登別+洞爺湖3日2夜&gt;函館4日3夜&gt;札幌+小樽4日3夜<br />\n係咪咁樣會比較好D?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去余市加小樽果日應該做鐵路撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bbd301ca6764bf992d6dc8f37f733f1516b2c58","tid":523982,"uid":20759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9c04d0bc75d00c3f1c3f5bb0663de6d1b41b64a","tid":523982,"uid":44783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:49:08.000Z","msg":"望樓noguchi <br />\n我都想試, 但一晚3000幾, 唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T08:06:51.000Z","msg":"剛剛住完 好撚正 樓中樓有私人風呂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0649433ec1cb9c2891bfb7eae5d64f81907efcf","tid":523982,"uid":61535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc